Checks if the multiplicity of the to be chosen containers is 0..1  indicating that each time a choice is performed you can only choose exactly one of these to be chosen containers at a time.

Checks if the upperMultiplicity of the ChoiceContainerDef does specify how often the choice can be performed. If the upperMultiplicity of the ChoiceContainerDef is greater than 1 the sum of the chosen containers has to be considered.

Checks if the'defaultValue' of EcucLinkerSymbolDef start with a letter or a special character (sc) followed by upper- and lower-case letters or digits and special characters : identifier := (letter | sc) ( letter | digit | sc )* where letter is [a-z] or [A-Z] or sc is ( _ | .| $ | % ) and digit is [0-9].

Checks is the'defaultValue' of EcucStringParamDef start with a letter or a special character (sc) followed by upper- and lower-case letters or digits and special characters: identifier := (letter | sc) ( letter | digit | sc )* where letter is [a-z] or [A-Z] or sc is ( _ | . | $ | % ) and digit is [0-9].
